15
00:00:48,030 --> 00:00:50,305
The definition of "kkondae" is...

16
00:00:50,329 --> 00:00:53,500
slang for
an old person or a teacher.

17
00:00:54,769 --> 00:00:56,000
Peek-a-boo.

18
00:00:56,740 --> 00:00:58,275
You should sit here.

19
00:00:58,299 --> 00:00:59,516
