No.

207
00:13:37,630 --> 00:13:38,699
Are you okay?

208
00:13:38,799 --> 00:13:40,400
Sir. Sir!

209
00:13:43,669 --> 00:13:44,770
Darn it.

210
00:13:45,669 --> 00:13:49,709
You won't even let me die in peace!
Stop torturing me.

211
