to act up like this?

406
00:30:42,170 --> 00:30:43,439
- Hello.
- Hey.

407
00:30:44,080 --> 00:30:45,585
Hello.

408
00:30:45,609 --> 00:30:47,425
- Hello.
- Hello.

409
00:30:47,449 --> 00:30:49,226
- Hello.
- Good morning, Mr. Lee.

410
00:30:49,250 --> 00:30:50,855
- So you scored over 100 yesterday?
