00:32:20,940 --> 00:32:22,446
- Mr. Lee!
- Mr. Lee!

438
00:32:22,470 --> 00:32:25,116
- Mr. Lee!
- My gosh, stop it.

439
00:32:25,140 --> 00:32:27,356
- Mr. Lee!
- Mr. Lee!

